                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6368" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1000</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9066 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">负债万亿集团的涅槃重生——海航集团破产重整之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Nirvana Rebirth of the Debt Trillion Group - The Road to Bankruptcy and Reorganization of HNA Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汪金祥，吴陈碧，王晨浠，史烁祺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航集团；破产重整；中小股东权益</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HNA Group ；Bankruptcy Reorganization；Minority shareholders&#39; equity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海航集团有限公司是一家以航空运输主业为核心的跨国企业集团，其多元化的战略扩张使得公司规模急速发展，旗下核心企业海航控股也一跃成为国内四大航空公司之一。然而，由于海航缺乏应对宏观政策变动的有效措施，以及行业环境特点与公司治理混乱等原因，2017年海航集团出现了偿债危机，并且于2021年1月29日被债权人申请破产重整。本文从破产重整的原因及重整实施的角度对海航集团的破产重整进行详细分析，激发学员对我国公司治理、债务危机、破产重整及中小投资者权益保护等相关问题展开讨论。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">HNA Group Co., Ltd. is a multinational enterprise group with the core business of air transportation. Its diversified strategic expansion has made the company grow rapidly, and its core enterprise, Hainan Airlines, has become one of the four major domestic airlines. However, due to HNA&#39;s lack of effective measures to deal with macro policy changes, as well as the characteristics of the industry environment and the chaos of corporate governance, HNA Group had a debt repayment crisis in 2017 and was applied for bankruptcy reorganization by creditors on January 29, 2021. This paper analyzes the bankruptcy and reorganization of HNA Group in detail from the perspective of the reasons for bankruptcy and reorganization and the implementation of the reorganization, and stimulate students to discuss issues related to China&#39;s corporate governance, debt crisis, bankruptcy reorganization and the protection of the rights and interests of small and medium-sized investors.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司战略与风险管理》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业债务危机的定义与形成原因；企业破产重整的定义与价值；企业破产重整的举措与及其特点；破产重整中股东权益调整的方式与种类；SWOT模型；企业破产重整风险的预防策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-07</td>
                            </tr>
